Package: RANN2
Type: Package
Title: Fast Nearest Neighbour Search (Rcpp wrapper of Arya and Mount's libANN)
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-08-06
Author: Sunil Arya and David Mount (for ANN), Gregory Jefferis
Copyright: ANN library is copyright University of Maryland and Sunil Arya and
    David Mount. See file COPYRIGHT for details.
Maintainer: Gregory Jefferis <jefferis@gmail.com>
Description: Finds the k nearest neighbours for every point in a given dataset
    in O(N log N) time using Arya and Mount's ANN library (v1.1.3). This wrapper
    uses Rcpp to simplify access compared with the original RANN library.
License: GPL (>=3)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: https://github.com/jefferis/RANN2
Suggests:
    testthat
